718452f-a.folder: Central Park West & 67th Street, Manhattan, NY
718452f-a.text:
Central Park West, west side, from 67th to 68th Streets. In the centre, demolition work is about to begin on the Town House Apartments. Beyond it, on the S.W. corner of 68th Street, may be seen the Second Church of Christ Scientist. In the foreground, the sidewalk and street has been torn up for construction work on the Eighth Avenue subway.

September 24, 1928.

P.L. Sperr, Photographer.
